## Summary
This project successfully demonstrates the development of a **Gym Membership Management System** using Django. It covers environment setup, project creation, app modularization, URL routing, database design, and admin dashboard integration. The system provides a practical solution for managing gym operations, ensuring efficiency in handling members, trainers, subscriptions, attendance, and payments.  

All files (`manage.py`, apps, `requirements.txt`, ERD diagram, and documentation) have been organized and pushed to GitHub in the `gym_system/` repository for submission.

